WEBVTT

00:08:59.839 --> 00:09:01.277
RK: Twenty thirties.
CA: Sorry?

00:09:01.301 --> 00:09:02.821
RK: Twenty thirties.

00:09:02.845 --> 00:09:04.014
CA: Damn!

00:09:04.038 --> 00:09:06.002
I'm always 100 years late for everything.

00:09:06.026 --> 00:09:09.909
RK: Well, we did put social
security in in the 1930s.

00:09:09.933 --> 00:09:12.474
CA: It's a lot easier to make
predictions of the past.

00:09:12.498 --> 00:09:18.147
By the early 2030s, Western countries --
or richer countries, shall we say --

00:09:18.171 --> 00:09:22.218
will be rolling out UBIs,
universal basic income,

00:09:22.242 --> 00:09:26.077
enough for all of their citizens
to live comfortably.

00:09:26.101 --> 00:09:29.394
And by the end of the 2030s,